{"id":315462,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-刘春杰等8访民被警察保安殴打反遭刑事拘/","date":"2013-09-27T04:18:52Z","modified":"2013-09-27T04:18:52Z","title":"维权网 | 刘春杰等8访民被警察保安殴打反遭刑事拘留（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员柴民报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日中午，把物品寄存在马家楼的访民刘春杰等人上访回来后发现，寄存在这里的物品被当值的保安拿走，衣服等不值钱的物品被扔进了垃圾堆，贵重物品现金手机等不翼而飞。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在报警、打市长热线都无回音的情况下，他们去找保安理论。不料却遭到三十多名警察、保安对去讲理的访民拳打脚踢达十几分钟，当场有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>名访民（五男三女）被打倒在地，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>人全部被</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">120</span><span>送进医院，经鉴定五人轻伤、三人轻微伤，刘春杰被鉴定为轻微伤，而他咨询专家的结果是应为轻伤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>简单的治疗后，北京警方竟倒打一耙以“寻衅滋事”的罪名把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>位访民刑事拘留一个月后，等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>位访民的伤也快好了时，警方才把他们放出来。需要说明的是，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>位访民都没有在任何法律文书上签名，因为他们认为被关进看守所的应该是殴打他们的警察和保安。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在刑拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>天后，北京警方给刘春杰等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>位访民办了取保候审手续，但</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>位访民拒绝离开看守所，最后他们被警察强行驱赶出来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>出来时，北京警方对他们说，不要告了，向你们道歉，用钱解决吧。被访民拒绝。刘春杰表示，要求依法查处北京市公安局丰台分局马家楼派出所、玉泉营派出所滥用职权、暴力执法、严重侵害人权的违法行为。有关部门不依法解决，决不罢休。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>以下是他自己的控诉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uofoBdCjPlY/UkTcemmnyrI/AAAAAAAAous/eK75sWhLdZE/s1600/IMG_5265.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uofoBdCjPlY/UkTcemmnyrI/AAAAAAAAous/eK75sWhLdZE/s320/IMG_5265.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-EJBQxkrG-hI/UkTb1NzJJpI/AAAAAAAAot8/cRAvinoL2T4/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+002.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-EJBQxkrG-hI/UkTb1NzJJpI/AAAAAAAAot8/cRAvinoL2T4/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+002.jpg\" width=\"249\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cNrUWdqx-uw/UkTb2neFIVI/AAAAAAAAouE/Tvf9MKbyjJM/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+003.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cNrUWdqx-uw/UkTb2neFIVI/AAAAAAAAouE/Tvf9MKbyjJM/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+003.jpg\" width=\"244\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-T0KrqhHTvUo/UkTb7sdyotI/AAAAAAAAouY/ivKNUAgmhNA/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+004.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-T0KrqhHTvUo/UkTb7sdyotI/AAAAAAAAouY/ivKNUAgmhNA/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+004.jpg\" width=\"245\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-d54Fu-FqUkk/UkTb5JymJaI/AAAAAAAAouM/lvoFN8ojoqg/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+005.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-d54Fu-FqUkk/UkTb5JymJaI/AAAAAAAAouM/lvoFN8ojoqg/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+005.jpg\" width=\"225\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SUJFb7CClcg/UkTb7Lw0j-I/AAAAAAAAouU/SP7unDopAWk/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+006.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SUJFb7CClcg/UkTb7Lw0j-I/AAAAAAAAouU/SP7unDopAWk/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+006.jpg\" width=\"242\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nqCA9-ywGbU/UkTb-LmMk3I/AAAAAAAAouk/jG7paQDtXfQ/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87007.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" sr